Package: followr
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Title: Tidy data from the Follow The Money API
Description: The Follow the Money API 
<https://followthemoney.org/our-data/apis/> provides programmatic access to data
on political contributions for state elections.  The 'followr' package wraps 
this API and returns the data as tidy data frames that are suitbale for futher 
analysis and manipulation with packages from the 'tidyverse'.  This package is 
not officially supported by Follow the Money, it's parent organization The 
National Institute on Money in State Politics <https://www.followthemoney.org/>, 
or the Tidyverse. 
